oard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> I got the 100K ponee, and I don't regret it <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> (I got lucky and put together and sold PoTC kits when the prices were two to three times higher than they are now)</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.<br>
